uction Schemes (Prescribed Requirements) (England) (Amendment) Regulations 2026">The Council Tax Reduction Schemes (Prescribed Requirements) (England) (Amendment) Regulations 2026 (S.I. 2026/27)</Citation>, <CitationSubRef CitationRef="c3moim6v6-00018" id="c3moim6v6-00019" SectionRef="regulation-1-1" URI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2026/27/regulation/1/1">regs. 1(1)</CitationSubRef>, <CitationSubRef CitationRef="c3moim6v6-00018" id="c3moim6v6-00020" SectionRef="regulation-7-b" URI="http://www.legislation.gov.uk/id/uksi/2026/27/regulation/7/b" Operative="true">7(b)</CitationSubRef></Text></Para></Commentary></Commentaries></Legislation>